<plot>Exiled scientist Anton Schoenheim is determined to find a cure for ED-40, a drug that changed the world. His obsession takes him across the boundaries of scientific and medical ethics as he clones a child to fulfill his mission. His creation is Ludwig, a boy out of his time, who must discover if his destiny lies in the hands of fate, or if he can change his path and live a life of love and hope.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063220</url></doc>
